  "text": "Immunoblotting was performed as previously described [CITATION_1] . In brief, 50-100 μg total protein was applied to the gels followed by the addition of first and second antibodies conjugated with horseradish peroxidase. Images were analyzed with Quantity One software (Bio-Rad).",
